Package: PerfOMICS
Type: Package
Title: Athletic Performance Predictor
Version: 1.1.0
Author: Helena Jovic
Maintainer: The package maintainer <helena.jovic@mail.utoronto.ca>
Description: PerfOMICS is an R package that predicts athletic performance 
    scores using user-provided data on major genetic variants known to be 
    associated with specific aspects of sports performance to help profile 
    athletes in terms of endurance, power and speed ability and predict and 
    forecast effects of training programs. This R package also analyses the
    relationship between genetic score and cardiovascular fitness (VO2 max).
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
